---
title: Soy and Honey Chicken with Green Beans and Rice
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Soy & Honey Chicken, Green Beans & Rice in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/soy-and-honey-chicken-922b17fc-5539623c.jpg
